    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 134</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 1st</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1,000 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This ability can only be placed on composite bows. An <em>adaptive </em>bow responds to the strength of its wielder, acting as a bow with a strength rating equal to its wielder's Strength bonus. The wielder can fire it with a lesser Strength bonus (and cause less damage) if desired.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>warp wood</em>; <strong>Price</strong> +500 gp</p>",
